d":"132","parent":"131","text":"c-ANCA/PR3 → GPA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"p-ANCA/MPO → GEPA, vasculitis por levamisol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Dual positivo (PR3+MPO) → SOSPECHA COCAINA/LEVAMISOL","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"127","text":"ANA, anti-dsDNA, complemento → LES","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"127","text":"Anti-colágeno tipo II → policondritis (baja disponibilidad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"127","text":"ECA (enzima convertidora de angiotensina) → sarcoidosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"127","text":"VDRL/RPR + FTA-Abs → sifilis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"127","text":"PPD/IGRA (QuantiFERON) → tuberculosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"127","text":"Serologia VIH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"127","text":"Serologias especificas segun sospecha (Leishmania)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"127","text":"Screening toxicologico en orina → cocaina, metabolitos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"127","text":"LDH, beta-2 microglobulina → linfoma","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"112","text":"IMAGENES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"TC de cavidades paranasales\\N(cortes finos, sin/con contraste)","guid":"tgQWJxr-yCrEQefHRiq_Hg","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Extension osea de la necrosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Compromiso sinusal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"Erosion de base de craneo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"RNM de macizo facial →\\Nmejor definicion de partes\\Nblandas","guid":"Zdc342vh3Bhc65WbpuXIpA","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Invasion perineural (neoplasia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Extension intracraneal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"144","text":"TC de torax → nodulos pulmonares (GPA), infiltrados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"144","text":"Radiografia de torax → screening inicial","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"112","text":"BIOPSIA → OBLIGATORIA\\Nsi causa no clara","guid":"tuTjpZ2CWTFqhEywS3XCDA","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Biopsia de bordes de perforacion/ulcera","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"MULTIPLES MUESTRAS de distintos sitios → aumenta rendimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"Solicitar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Histopatologia convencional (H&E)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Tinciones especiales (PAS, Grocott, Ziehl-Neelsen, Fite-Faraco)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Inmunohistoquimica (CD56, CD3, CD20, Ki-67, VEB-EBER)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"157","text":"Cultivo de tejido (bacterias, hongos, micobacterias)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"154","text":"Patron histologico\\Norientador","guid":"hsqyLecqmlN8L06QhcTpUg","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Granulomas caseificantes → TB, hongos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Granulomas no caseificantes → sarcoidosis, GPA (con vasculitis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"Vasculitis necrotizante → GPA, GEPA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"162","text":"Necrosis coagulativa + hifas → mucormicosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"162","text":"Infiltrado linfoide atipico → linfoma NK/T","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"162","text":"Necrosis inespecifica + material birrefringente → cocaina","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"0","text":"Diagnostico\\NDiferencial\\NSistematizado","guid":"22mDGBm1PMhGjd0qxL7YZg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Enfoque por\\NPATRON\\NCLINICO","guid":"BP9TnhEOL_xnKumYBtyUAA","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis + compromiso sistemico → GPA, GEPA, LES, linfoma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis + infeccion → TB, sifilis, mucormicosis, Leishmania","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis + uso de sustancias → cocaina (CIMDL), vasoconstrictores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis + masa/tumor → linfoma NK/T, carcinoma, melanoma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis aislada + antecedente quirurgico → iatrogénica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"170","text":"Necrosis + DM descompensada → MUCORMICOSIS primero","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"169","text":"CLAVES\\NDIFERENCIALES","guid":"XROfHcscNU8ymwfNeeoYnA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"GPA vs CIMDL\\N(cocaina)","guid":"KK_4l7vWEjR86jPm6BXuIQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"Ambos → costras, perforacion, c-ANCA puede ser (+) en ambos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"GPA → compromiso renal/pulmonar, granulomas con vasculitis en biopsia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"CIMDL → dual ANCA (PR3+MPO), material birrefringente en biopsia, sin glomerulonefritis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"CRITICO → screening toxicologico SIEMPRE ante necrosis septal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"177","text":"GPA vs\\NLinfoma NK/T","guid":"fG9M-PgB8rfkp_9scMY64w","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Ambos → destruccion mediofacial progresiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"GPA → ANCA+, granulomas con vasculitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"Linfoma NK/T → CD56+, VEB-EBER+, necrosis angiocentrica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"177","text":"Mucormicosis vs\\Notras causas","guid":"fMdTXVw-ApQAxQt63xn4hw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Mucormicosis → progresion rapida (horas-dias), necrosis negra, DM/inmunosupresion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"Otras → progresion lenta (semanas-meses)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"PRINCIPIOS\\NGENERALES","guid":"9Ysx0n0wMTbKWG8lAu2kfA","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Tratar causa subyacente → PRIORIDAD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"Control de sintomas locales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"191","text":"Referir a equipo multidisciplinario (ORL + Reumatologia/Inmunologia/Oncologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"191","text":"En AM → considerar estado funcional, fragilidad, expectativa de vida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"Tratamiento\\Nespecifico por\\Ncausa","guid":"h7ISd9g2CPjt6fpKWJ0cSQ","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"GPA → corticoides + ciclofosfamida (induccion)\\N→ azatioprina (mantencion)","guid":"8KqGCFP-McJNS7YgFHBl9Q","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"Rituximab alternativa a ciclofosfamida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"Considerar toxicidad en AM (ciclofosfamida → cistitis, mielosupresion)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"Cocaina → cesacion absoluta + manejo local","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","text":"Mucormicosis → anfotericina B liposomal + debridamiento quirurgico URGENTE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"196","text":"Linfoma NK/T → quimioterapia (SMILE/DDGP) + radioterapia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"196","text":"TB → esquema RIPE (considerar interacciones en AM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"196","text":"Sifilis → penicilina G benzatina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"190","text":"Manejo local de la\\Nperforacion","guid":"4kOCWOeELYsyi0t6kPQGhA","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"Humidificacion nasal → suero fisiologico, gel nasal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"Retiro de costras con irrigacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"205","text":"Boton septal (obturador) → sintomatico, primera linea en AM fragil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"205","text":"Reparacion quirurgica → considerar solo si\\Ncausa controlada y buen estado funcional","guid":"pHdi0h_k7_qLcE1-HgoOjA","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"Colgajos mucoperiosticos bilaterales + injerto interpuesto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"Tasa de exito ~90% con tecnica endoscopica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"190","text":"Consideraciones\\Ngeriatricas\\Nespecificas","guid":"BTj_ohVHjBTC3WurZtgHDQ","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"FRAGILIDAD → CFS >=5 limita opciones quirurgicas agresivas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Polifarmacia → revisar anticoagulantes, anticolinergicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"Comorbilidad → DM, IRC, inmunosupresion modifican pronostico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"212","text":"DEPRESCRIPCION de vasoconstrictores topicos si uso cronico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"212","text":"Oxigenoterapia → SIEMPRE con humidificacion adecuada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"212","text":"Proporcionalidad terapeutica → en AM fragil, boton septal puede ser mejor que cirugia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClinicas","guid":"7O-sHO5HD4DYhvic5sY_0w","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"PREGUNTAR SIEMPRE por uso de cocaina → incluso en AM (CIMDL mimetiza GPA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Dual ANCA (PR3+MPO positivo) → alta sospecha de cocaina/levamisol mas que GPA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"Necrosis negra + DM descompensada = MUCORMICOSIS hasta demostrar lo contrario → EMERGENCIA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"Biopsia MULTIPLE de distintos sitios → un solo sitio puede no ser diagnostico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"219","text":"No cauterizar ambos lados del septum simultaneamente → riesgo de perforacion iatrogénica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"219","text":"Vasoconstrictores topicos >7 dias = factor de riesgo de necrosis en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"219","text":"En toda necrosis septal sin causa obvia → descartar linfoma NK/T (CD56, VEB)","guid":"E0DkSxEjXuiz475aJeviHQ","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"219","text":"Oxigenoterapia sin humidificacion → causa subestimada de xerosis y necrosis en AM hospitalizados","guid":"Olc8FMuSB3VCpcWsBP86uQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"219","text":"Mucosa nasal del AM ya comprometida por envejecimiento → umbral mas bajo para dano","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"219","text":"Boton septal = excelente opcion paliativa en AM fragil con perforacion sintomatica","guid":"ZrL0Ov8a2f6LEu8fuujGMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"1. Sardana K, Goel K. Nasal septal ulceration. Clin Dermatol. 2014;32(6):817-26","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"230","text":"2. Greco A et al. Clinic manifestations in granulomatosis with polyangiitis. Int J Immunopathol Pharmacol. 2015;29(2):151-9","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"230","text":"3. Berman M et al. Cocaine-Induced Vasculitis. Rambam Maimonides Med J. 2016;7(4):e0263","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"230","text":"4. Seyer BA et al. Aggressive destructive midfacial lesion from cocaine abuse. Oral Surg Oral Med Oral Pathol Oral Radiol Endod. 2002;94(4):465-70","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"230","text":"5. Gravina A et al. Endoscopic Techniques for Nasal Septal Perforation Repair: A Systematic Review. Ann Otol Rhinol Laryngol. 2022;132(5):527-535","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"230","text":"6. Devlin JW et al. Clinical Practice Guidelines for Prevention and Management of Pain, Agitation/Sedation, Delirium. Crit Care Med. 2018;46(9):e825-e873","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":236,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"NecrosisTabiqueNasal iPad","id":"map_824","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"NecrosisTabiqueNasal iPad"}